text:
Hey, everyone!
I am an exchange student from Brazil here in Netherlands. When I've found the "Yamaha GL1 TBS Guitalele gitaar-ukelele Tobacco Brown Sunburst" was love in the first sight!
It was incredible, fast delivery and high quality instrument!
Now I can play my Bossa Nova, Samba and Pagode in high style.
Peace, thanks!
